{
  "stem": "9262.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how antisemitic they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I experienced, when I went to school, I was beaten up by Polish boys, just like in Germany also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jew boy, Jew pig.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And three or four people would fight me, and I was one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the first day, I had to run in order to evade them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although they caught up with me and one or two really hit me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I managed to hit one of them, knock him on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I sort of kicked him in the groin, and he fell, and I ran.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the following day, my brother, who worked in the vicinity, used to be my guard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he came, nobody dared to attack us because he just took one of them, and he was shaking him, and he was dancing around, and he couldn't catch his breath.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said to the others, this fellow is a strong Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Better keep away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was endemic in the population.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Poles who worked for Jews, although they were paid for doing the job because jobs were very scarce, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] still had a hatred.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were washing the clothes, the laundry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Jewish woman would pay them, would give them bread, would give them a meal, would give them tea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would say, thank you very much, get their money, and then they would go out, and would say, bloody Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The day will come when they will work for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what they used to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My uncle had a servant, Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She must have been about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in her late twenties.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was cooking and cleaning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, my cousin and his sister were not big eaters.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
